Simba, a nine-month-old lion cub, has been enjoying the company of humans after being saved from its mother, which tried to eat it.




Dominique and Juliette Cases own a small private zoo in Casteil, southwestern France, but Simba has been welcomed in the comforts of their home due to its young age.



